snippet.title: DSD
snippet.description: This channel is focused on helping people survive when divorcing a narcissistic ex when kids are involved.  Breaking free from a narcissistic abusive relationship is complicated enough but when you add kids into the mix what are you supposed to do? This site will strive to answer those questions and provide you real-world experience to help you through the process.
